"freebsd# during the initial system setup.  Documentation may also be installed later using packages:"
msgstr ""
"所有受支持的 FreeBSD 版本都在安装程序中提供了一个选项，即在最初的系统设置中在 [.filename]#/usr/local/share/doc/freebsd# 下安装额外的文档。文档也"
"可以在以后使用软件包来安装："

#. type: delimited block . 4
